OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775235955
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the John
OL,4,CSwinney leader interview
OL,6,FITV Border will be sitting down with
OL,7,Fall the main political party leaders
OL,8,Fduring the Holyrood election campaign.
OL,10,FThe first interview was with the SNP's
OL,11,FJohn Swinney. Here are three things we
OL,12,Flearned.
OL,14,FThe south of Scotland is crucial
OL,16,FThere is a "blue belt" on Scotland's
OL,17,Fpolitical landscape that covers the
OL,18,Fcountry's dividing line with England.
OL,26,@xD@LOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
