PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775235955
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the John
OL,4,CSwinney leader interview
OL,6,FJohn Swinney knows he needs to turn at
OL,7,Fleast some of that yellow if he is to
OL,8,Fachieve his aim of gaining a majority
OL,9,Fat Holyrood.
OL,11,FHe said: "The three seats along the
OL,12,Fborder in the south of Scotland are
OL,13,Fpivotal to the outcome of the election.
OL,15,F"I will go into this election focusing
OL,16,Fon winning a majority in the Scottish
OL,17,Fparliament so I can take forward the
OL,18,Fagenda of the SNP, which is the agenda
OL,19,Fof the people of Scotland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775235955
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the John
OL,4,CSwinney leader interview
OL,6,F"And I recognise the importance of
OL,7,Fwinning in the south of Scotland and
OL,8,Fwinning in those constituencies so
OL,9,Fthey have good strong SNP campaigns
OL,10,Fwith good strong SNP candidates and
OL,11,FI'm very optimistic about our
OL,12,Fprospects in those three seats."
OL,14,FOn a national swing, the Conservatives
OL,15,Flook vulnerable, particularly with the
OL,16,Frise of Reform UK.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775235955
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the John
OL,4,CSwinney leader interview
OL,6,FBut the Tories have a well-drilled
OL,7,Flocal operation and the fact they know
OL,8,Fthey will lose MSPs in other parts of
OL,9,Fthe country means there is an
OL,10,Fincreased focus ` and additional
OL,11,Fresources ` on the region.
OL,13,FSmall shifts could make a huge
OL,14,Fdifference during the campaign and the
OL,15,Fsouthern seats should be closely
OL,16,Fwatched.
OL,18,FNHS record will dog the first minister
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
