PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775235955
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the John
OL,4,CSwinney leader interview
OL,6,FAny party that has been in power for
OL,7,F19 years will have weak spots in its
OL,8,Frecord.
OL,10,FNo one can manage a spotless
OL,11,Fperformance over that amount of time
OL,12,Fin government and the SNP's opponents
OL,13,Fsee lengthy NHS waiting times as a
OL,14,Fparticular weakness.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775235955
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the John
OL,4,CSwinney leader interview
OL,6,FDuring the 2024 budget, the first of
OL,7,FSwinney's time in charge of the
OL,8,FScottish government, a promise was
OL,9,Fmade that "by March 2026, no one will
OL,10,Fwait longer than 12 months for a new
OL,11,Foutpatient appointment, inpatient
OL,12,Ftreatment or day case treatment".
OL,14,FThere was anger in the upper echelons
OL,15,Fof the Scottish government last
OL,16,FSeptember when health secretary Neil
OL,17,FGray called that promise an
OL,18,F"aspiration" rather than a cast-iron
OL,19,Fguarantee.
OL,26,@tD@`O]zD@AOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775235955
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the John
OL,4,CSwinney leader interview
OL,6,FSwinney himself said he could
OL,7,F"recommit" to the promise in the days
OL,8,Fthat followed but the deadline has
OL,9,Fcome and gone and the first minister
OL,10,Fadmitted on Tuesday it will "take us
OL,11,Fjust a little bit longer" to meet the
OL,12,Ftarget.
OL,14,FHe said: "Let's look at the data. Nine
OL,15,Fmonths in a row we've seen a reduction
OL,16,Fin outpatient long waits. There's been
OL,17,Fa reduction since the summer of last
OL,18,Fyear of 63% in long waits,
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@JO]rD@]OUsD@YO]vD@JOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775235955
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the John
OL,4,CSwinney leader interview
OL,6,F"So I accept the task is not completed
OL,7,Fbut it will be completed very very
OL,8,Fshortly. But fundamentally there's
OL,9,Fbeen a rise in the number of
OL,10,Fprocedures undertaken in the NHS, a
OL,11,Fbig reduction in the number of long
OL,12,Fwaits people experience - either for
OL,13,Foutpatient or inpatient appointments.
OL,15,F"So by any dispassionate assessment,
OL,16,Fthe SNP government has delivered huge
OL,17,Fimprovements in the National Health
OL,18,FService, meeting the needs of the
OL,19,Fpublic."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775235955
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the John
OL,4,CSwinney leader interview
OL,6,FWhen pushed on the fact that he didn't
OL,7,Fpromise improvements, he promised an
OL,8,Fend to year-long waits, Swinney
OL,9,Fresponded: "I'm simply saying it's
OL,10,Fgoing to take us just a little bit
OL,11,Flonger to do that. And that's all it
OL,12,Fis, a little bit longer.
OL,14,F"But fundamentally huge progress has
OL,15,Fbeen made, great improvements have
OL,16,Fbeen made in the National Health
OL,17,FService.
OL,19,F"The NHS has turned a corner under my
OL,20,Fleadership, delivering for the people
OL,21,Fof Scotland."
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775235955
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the John
OL,4,CSwinney leader interview
OL,6,FYou can see the opportunity that
OL,7,Fopposition parties see in attacking
OL,8,Fthe SNP's record from their reaction
OL,9,Fto our interview.
OL,11,FAnalysis of the main 17 pledges of the
OL,12,F2021 SNP manifesto by ITV Border `
OL,13,Fwhich matches work carried out by
OL,14,Fother media ` show that only around
OL,15,Fone-third of them can be said to be
OL,16,Fdelivered in full.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775235955
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the John
OL,4,CSwinney leader interview
OL,6,FScottish Labour issued a press release
OL,7,Fwhere its deputy leader Jackie Baillie
OL,8,Fsaid: "John Swinney and the SNP have
OL,9,Fbroken one promise after another and
OL,10,Fit is insulting to pretend otherwise."
OL,12,FThe problem opposition parties face is
OL,13,Fthat even with unhappiness at the
OL,14,FSNP's record in power, people have not
OL,15,Fshifted their backing to the
OL,16,Falternatives on offer.
OL,18,FLeadership on fuel panic buying
OL,26,@pD@GOUrD@fO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775235955
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the John
OL,4,CSwinney leader interview
OL,6,FSwinney moved to assure people and
OL,7,Fstave off panic buying as motorists
OL,8,Fstarted queuing at petrol stations
OL,9,Facross Scotland with people beginning
OL,10,Fto worry about fuel shortages.
OL,12,FAsked what he would say to anyone
OL,13,Fgoing to fill up the tank because
OL,14,Fthey're worried, he said: "I just
OL,15,Fwould ask people to be patient and
OL,16,Fcautious and to go about their lives
OL,17,Fin the way they normally would do
OL,18,Fbecause that way we can maintain the
OL,19,Fsupplies of everything within our
OL,20,Fcountry, if we have the normal
OL,21,Fapproach to our purchasing patterns.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775235955
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the John
OL,4,CSwinney leader interview
OL,6,F"Now I accept that people will be
OL,7,Fanxious. I totally understand that
OL,8,Fanxiety. But if people just go about
OL,9,Fthings in the normal fashion, we'll be
OL,10,Fokay."
OL,12,FThe war in Iran has led to spikes in
OL,13,Fthe cost of energy and fuel with the
OL,14,FRAC saying the average diesel prices
OL,15,Fat UK forecourts on Tuesday were
OL,16,F182.8p per litre, up 40p since the
OL,17,Fstart of the conflict in the Middle
OL,18,FEast on February 28.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775235955
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the John
OL,4,CSwinney leader interview
OL,6,FThe average cost of petrol is 152.8p
OL,7,Fper litre, an increase of 20p since
OL,8,Fthe conflict began.
OL,10,FOil prices ` which have a significant
OL,11,Feffect on the cost of wholesale fuel `
OL,12,Fhave soared in response to Iran's
OL,13,Fstranglehold on tankers passing
OL,14,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,16,FThis has led to concerns about
OL,17,Fshortages, although prices fell on
OL,18,FWednesday morning to below $100 a
OL,19,Fbarrel.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775235955
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the John
OL,4,CSwinney leader interview
OL,6,FAt a press conference on Wednesday,
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer said the UK would
OL,8,Fhost an international summit aimed at
OL,9,Freopening the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,11,FHe said the UK government was closely
OL,12,Fmonitoring the situation when asked
OL,13,Fwhether people should consider
OL,14,Fchanging their behaviour in response
OL,15,Fto the increasing economic pressures.
OL,17,FSwinney is clearly keen to be involved
OL,18,Fin the situation to ensure people are
OL,19,Foffered the best information about the
OL,20,Fsituation.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G15/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775235955
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the John
OL,4,CSwinney leader interview
OL,6,FHe said he has been offered a four
OL,7,Fnations briefing with the leaders of
OL,8,Fthe other devolved administrations in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland and Wales but that no
OL,10,Fdate has been set.
OL,12,FBut he is not above playing politics
OL,13,Fwith the situation as the election
OL,14,Fapproaches.
OL,16,FIn a press release issued by the SNP
OL,17,Fon Wednesday morning, Swinney accused
OL,18,Fthe UK government of "sleepwalking
OL,19,Finto a potentially unprecedented
OL,20,Fcrisis because of a "lack of real
OL,21,Faction".
OL,26,@zD@VOU|D@UOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G16/17
